    "description": "Possession Obsession is a 2-4 player local multiplayer party game. As interns, you and your friends will compete for a coveted position at the infamous HELLC. Utilize your demonic powers and possess mortals to complete the boss's tasks in any way possible.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MOUNDS OF MORTALS TO POSSESS!</strong></h2>Possess mortals at any time! Gain special abilities from whomever you possess to help you complete the HELLC's tasks and impede the progress of your fellow interns. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/81ecd1265919e56a0ef7c76f2b801aeb.poster.avif?t=1658517457\" width=608 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/81ecd1265919e56a0ef7c76f2b801aeb.webm?t=1658517457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/81ecd1265919e56a0ef7c76f2b801aeb.mp4?t=1658517457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4 DIFFERENT DEMONIC CLASSES</strong></h2>Make use of 4 unique classes to crush the competition. Each class has access to 2 abilities in demon form and another when possession a mortal. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/a18ad39d0697e1e2724202a7ee284e56.poster.avif?t=1658517457\" width=608 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/a18ad39d0697e1e2724202a7ee284e56.webm?t=1658517457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/a18ad39d0697e1e2724202a7ee284e56.mp4?t=1658517457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FRIENDSHIP RUINING TASKS TO FIGHT OVER!</strong></h2>Fight over the many tasks the HELLC assigns to be the intern that gets the job!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/b18529dd7e11bf68a5948e6a5b1eb50b.poster.avif?t=1658517457\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/b18529dd7e11bf68a5948e6a5b1eb50b.webm?t=1658517457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838030/extras/b18529dd7e11bf68a5948e6a5b1eb50b.mp4?t=1658517457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
